            <h1>Installing on MAC OS X</h1>
            <p>The Embedthis Expansive install distribution for Mac OS X is published as a an installable pkg file.</p>

            <a id="pkg"></a>
            <h2>Installing the PKG Image</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Double click on the PKG image.</li>
            </ol>

            <a id="removing"></a>
            <h2>Removing Expansive</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Run a terminal and change directory to the installation directory for Expansive. </li>
                <li>Run the remove script in the install directory for Expansive by typing:</li>
            </ol>
            <pre class="ui code segment">
sudo ./uninstall
</pre>

            <p>You can run exp via:</p>
            <pre class="ui code segment">
exp
</pre>
            <p>To get all the options for Expansive read the man page via:</p>
            <pre class="ui code segment">
man exp
</pre>or get the command help via:
            <pre class="ui code segment">
exp --help
</pre>
